    <div id="slide2" class="slide" data-background="#60a5fa">
        <div class="content-box">
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Who Was He?</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Al-Khwarizmi (c. 780 – c. 850 CE) was a Persian polymath who lived and worked at the House of Wisdom in Baghdad during the Islamic Golden Age. He made foundational contributions to mathematics, astronomy, and geography. His work was pivotal in bridging ancient knowledge with the modern world.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center space-x-4">
