        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Slide 4: Algorithms and Numerals -->
    <div id="slide4" class="slide" data-background="#1d4ed8">
        <div class="content-box">
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Algorithms and Numerals</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed mb-6">
                The word **"algorithm"** is a Latinized version of Al-Khwarizmi's name. His work on Hindu-Arabic numerals was crucial in introducing the decimal system, including the concept of zero, to Europe. This provided a far more efficient way to perform calculations.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center space-y-4">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/350x200/93c5fd/000?text=Illustration+of+Abacus+and+Numerals" alt="Illustration of an abacus next to Hindu-Arabic numerals" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-200 mt-2">
                    A conceptual illustration of the shift from counting boards to the modern decimal system.
                </p>
                <a href="https://ioinformatics.org/journal/v11si_2017_71_74.pdf" target="_blank" class="resource-button inline-block mt-4">Read about Al-Khwarizmi and algorithms</a>
